{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":false,"flaws":{},"title":"DedicatedWorkerGlobalScope: message event","mdn_url":"/de/docs/Web/API/DedicatedWorkerGlobalScope/message_event","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/DedicatedWorkerGlobalScope\"><code>DedicatedWorkerGlobalScope</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Eigenschaften</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DedicatedWorkerGlobalScope/name\"><code>name</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Methoden</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DedicatedWorkerGlobalScope/close\"><code>close()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DedicatedWorkerGlobalScope/postMessage\"><code>postMessage()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Ereignisse</summary><ol><li><em><code>message</code></em></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DedicatedWorkerGlobalScope/messageerror_event\"><code>messageerror</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Vererbung:</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope\"><code>WorkerGlobalScope</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p><font><font>Das&nbsp;</font></font><code>message</code><font><font>Ereignis wird auf ein&nbsp;</font></font><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DedicatedWorkerGlobalScope\"><code>DedicatedWorkerGlobalScope</code></a><font><font>Objekt&nbsp;</font><font>ausgelöst,&nbsp;</font><font>wenn der Worker eine Nachricht von seinem übergeordneten Objekt empfängt (dh wenn der übergeordnete Benutzer eine Nachricht sendet mit&nbsp;</font></font><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Worker/postMessage\">Worker.postMessage()</a></code><font><font>).</font></font></p>\n\n<table class=\"properties\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Bubbles</th>\n   <td>No</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Cancelable</th>\n   <td>No</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Interface</th>\n   <td><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/MessageEvent\"><code>MessageEvent</code></a></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Event handler property</th>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DedicatedWorkerGlobalScope/message_event\">onmessage</a></code></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"examples","title":"Examples","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Dieser Code erstellt einen neuen Worker und sendet ihm eine Nachricht mit <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Worker/postMessage\">Worker.postMessage()</a></code>:</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> worker <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Worker</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"static/scripts/worker.js\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\nworker<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'message'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">event</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=&gt;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">Received message from worker: </span><span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">${</span>event<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>data<span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n\n<p>Der Worker kann auf diese Nachricht warten, indem er <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/EventTarget/addEventListener\">addEventListener()</a></code>&nbsp;verwendet:</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token comment\">// inside static/scripts/worker.js</span>\n\nself<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'message'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">event</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=&gt;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">Received message from parent: </span><span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">${</span>event<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>data<span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n\n<p>Alternativ könnte er es mit der <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DedicatedWorkerGlobalScope/message_event\">onmessage</a></code> <font>Event-Handler-Eigenschaft&nbsp;</font><font>abhören</font>:</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token comment\">// static/scripts/worker.js</span>\n\nself<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function-variable function\">onmessage</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">event</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=&gt;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">Received message from parent: </span><span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">${</span>event<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>data<span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications","title":"Specifications","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specification</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/indices.html#event-message\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" title=\"Die 'HTML Living Standard' Spezifikation\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard</a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Lebender Standard</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.DedicatedWorkerGlobalScope.message_event","dataURL":"/de/docs/Web/API/DedicatedWorkerGlobalScope/message_event/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"See also","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li>Verwandte Ereignisse: <code><a href=\"/docs/Web/API/DedicatedWorkerGlobalScope/messageerror_event\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\">messageerror</a></code>.</li>\n <li><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Worker/postMessage\">Worker.postMessage()</a></code>.</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Examples","id":"examples"},{"text":"Specifications","id":"specifications"},{"text":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"See also","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"Das messageEreignis wird auf ein DedicatedWorkerGlobalScopeObjekt ausgelöst, wenn der Worker eine Nachricht von seinem übergeordneten Objekt empfängt (dh wenn der übergeordnete Benutzer eine Nachricht sendet mit Worker.postMessage()).","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"DedicatedWorkerGlobalScope: message event","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"}],"source":{"folder":"de/web/api/dedicatedworkerglobalscope/message_event","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/de/web/api/dedicatedworkerglobalscope/message_event/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/de/docs/Web","title":"Webtechnologien für Entwickler"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API Referenz"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API/DedicatedWorkerGlobalScope","title":"DedicatedWorkerGlobalScope"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API/DedicatedWorkerGlobalScope/message_event","title":"DedicatedWorkerGlobalScope: message event"}],"pageTitle":"DedicatedWorkerGlobalScope: message event - Web API Referenz | MDN","noIndexing":false}}